# WAY qwertystock services

Treat `way.qwertystock.com` as our qwertystock subdomain. All services running
behind this host are part of the project infrastructure, but this host is not
the main sales website.

- Public host: `https://way.qwertystock.com`
- SSH alias: `way-fr`
- Host: `37.187.57.177`
- SSH user: `debian`
- SSH port: `22744`
- Local SSH key: `C:\Users\escho\.ssh\id_rsa_qwerty_vpn`
- WAY app/repo path: `/home/debian/qwertystock`

Known services on WAY:

- `qwertystock-way.service`
- `qwertystock_support_bot.service`
- Support chat: `https://way.qwertystock.com/support-chat/`
- Detectron: `https://way.qwertystock.com/detectron/`

Before changing any WAY service, first inspect current nginx, systemd, and
process state on the server. Multiple independent services share this one
domain, so do not assume a single app owns all routes.

Useful read-only inventory command:

```bash
ssh way-fr "hostname; systemctl --no-pager --type=service --state=running | grep -Ei 'qwertystock|support|nginx'; ps -eo pid,user,cmd --sort=cmd | grep -Ei 'detectron|way|support|python|node' | grep -v grep"
```

Do not treat `way.qwertystock.com` as the primary product/sales site. The main
sales website remains `https://qwertystock.com` on `145.239.0.57`.
